snippet.title: Johnny Depp and Amber Heard's hilarious 'apology' isn't going to win any Oscars | Page Six
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp and his wife, Amber Heard, issued perhaps the most awkward apology video of all time after Heard pleaded guilty to smuggling their two dogs into Australia. Page Six read between the lines of their statement and translated it for you here.
